1. Elastic Cloud on Azure (Managed Elasticsearch)

Why Elastic Cloud

âœ… Full Lucene support â€” analyzers, fuzziness, synonyms, token filters.

âœ… Official Phonetic Analysis Plugin supporting Soundex, Metaphone, Double-Metaphone.

âœ… Managed by Elastic, hosted in Azure regions with HA, snapshots, and automatic upgrades.

âœ… Elastic Query DSL is close to Azure Search syntax â†’ low migration effort.

ğŸ’° Cost control:

Scales horizontally via index sharding + replication.

Per-GB/month pricing is typically lower than Azure Search.

Can compress inverted index storage using Azure blob or SSD nodes.


âš™ï¸ Flexibility: allows replication of our custom analyzer stack (ASCII-folding, synonyms, token filters, phonetic filters).

ğŸŒ HA & DR: Supports multi-region failover across Azure zones.



