2. Apache Solr (Managed via SolrCloud or Self-Managed)

Key Highlights

ğŸ§© Beider-Morse Phonetic Matching (BMPM) â€” best-in-class phonetic matching built-in (no extra plugin).

ğŸ” Excellent for large datasets where phonetic grouping is required (millions + records).

âš™ï¸ Strong control over tokenization and phonetic pipeline.

ğŸ§® Ranking & boosting easily configurable.

âš ï¸ Requires manual ops for scaling (Zookeeper, shards, replication).


When to Choose

If maximum control and built-in phonetic support are priority, Solr + BMPM provides the strongest phonetic precision.


