ğŸ§Š Cold Path: For 1.36 B corpus, leverage durable function fan-out/fan-in for distributed batch scoring.

âš¡ Latency: Query evaluation happens on short phonetic codes â†’ response in few milliseconds.


Advantages

âœ… Full control over algorithmic logic.

âœ… Low infra cost (pay per compute + storage).

âœ… Can be hosted fully in Azure PaaS (Functions + SQL/Postgres).

âœ… Easy to extend with caching or Redis hybrid.


Trade-offs

âŒ Manual maintenance of phonetic rules and DB optimizations.

âŒ Not ideal for multi-tenant large-scale concurrency without additional partitioning strategy.



